{"tid":2005645,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傳國泰醞釀重組架構    研裁員縮航線整合品牌","createTime":"2020-05-07T08:42:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T09:13:30.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b828be33c9be72a2c01581d64e6494693bef98cf","tid":2005645,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T08:42:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/3uICDzaP4RtFtE7puIPiNg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUwO2g9NjAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20200507a130949.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F3uICDzaP4RtFtE7puIPiNg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUwO2g9NjAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20200507a130949.jpg&h=fd2affb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】由於預期未來兩三年的航空需求無法回到去年的水平，有報道指國泰航空正研究在疫情後重組架構，令公司業務及員工在未來，不會再受到如今次疫情般的災難性打擊。<br />\n<br />\n研究中的架構重組，包括減少職位、服務路線、機隊規模，和整合其他航空品牌。消息人士又指，國泰另擬推出新一輪的減薪金措施，如延長無薪假4周等。<br />\n<br />\n報道又指，國泰不擬申請政府的工資補貼計畫，因有關計畫需企業保證在補貼的半年期間不裁員。若公司申請該計畫，預期可獲18.4億，相等於每年人工開支的9%。"},{"pid":"2ab9f312550fe537e73fc07e483edfccbf95122f","tid":2005645,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T08:46:22.000Z","msg":"廣東人？"},{"pid":"0a3b5269edf7402c7423aa4fa117c469737cb0d7","tid":2005645,"uid":80452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T08:50:25.000Z","msg":"鳩估一句<br />\nit部門先開刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2080a731e82b2dd9b2169346490ba2ad1057d087","tid":2005645,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T08:50:38.000Z","msg":"垃圾紅企"},{"pid":"70a178f75d2e8aa948db35013bd22ab87cd7cf6e","tid":2005645,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a3b5269edf7402c7423aa4fa117c469737cb0d7","tid":2005645,"uid":80452,"like":1,"dislike